2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,320
[I Don't Want To Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:43,009 --> 00:01:43,970
Li Jin Bu.

4
00:01:44,770 --> 00:01:46,289
You're over-reacting.

5
00:01:46,570 --> 00:01:48,200
You can't be so vulnerable to criticism.

6
00:01:48,289 --> 00:01:49,039
I've told you that

7
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,600
