14
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,720
This is the rule.

15
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:00,290
The rule I set for you.

16
00:02:00,610 --> 00:02:01,490
Humph.

17
00:02:02,730 --> 00:02:03,840
Li Jin Bu.

18
00:02:03,930 --> 00:02:04,680
Come here.

19
00:02:04,770 --> 00:02:05,600
Repeat it.

20
00:02:05,690 --> 00:02:06,700
I ask you to repeat it.

21
00:02:07,170 --> 00:02:11,460
[Episode 4: This is my rule]

22
00:02:13,050 --> 00:02:14,360
What if he hits you?

23
00:02:14,450 --> 00:02:15,370
He wouldn't dare.

24
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,000
Don't worry.

25
00:02:17,090 --> 00:02:18,160
I don't beat girls.

26
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:19,150
No.

27
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,120
Don't go out.

28
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:22,920
Hurry up!

29
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,100
I think we should have...

30
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,520
That day...

31
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:27,840
Du.

32
00:02:27,930 --> 00:02:29,210
Egg!

33
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,470
What...

34
00:02:31,570 --> 00:02:33,380
Stand there. Go back.

35
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,600
What happened?

36
00:02:36,050 --> 00:02:36,930
Nothing.

37
00:02:39,790 --> 00:02:40,750
Chen Jun He.

38
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,640
We are at school.

39
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,700
Who are you?

40
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,210
It's none of your business.

41
00:02:47,110 --> 00:02:47,960
Calm down, buddy.

42
00:02:48,050 --> 00:02:48,960
Don't be angry.

43
00:02:49,050 --> 00:02:50,150
Move back.

44
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:53,350
He pushed me.

45
00:02:53,490 --> 00:02:54,450
So?

46
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:55,970
What are you doing, Mao? He pushed me.

47
00:02:56,170 --> 00:02:57,600
Sit down.

48
00:02:57,690 --> 00:02:58,700
What do you want to do?

49
00:02:58,790 --> 00:02:59,920
What do you want to do?

50
00:03:00,010 --> 00:03:01,210
What?

51
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:05,680
What are you doing?

52
00:03:05,790 --> 00:03:06,880
What are you doing?

53
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,440
Who is making trouble?

54
00:03:14,410 --> 00:03:15,400
Ms Yang.

55
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,640
Why are you dragging me?

56
00:03:16,730 --> 00:03:18,970
I just dropped by to say hi.

57
00:03:20,690 --> 00:03:21,570
Who?

58
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,570
Who pushed me?

59
00:03:26,210 --> 00:03:27,090
Who?

60
00:03:27,390 --> 00:03:28,270
Who?

61
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:34,640
Why didn't she hit others but you?

62
00:03:35,130 --> 00:03:36,320
I don't know either.

63
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,240
I was just about to ask her,

64
00:03:37,329 --> 00:03:38,760
but you came and dragged me out.

65
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:40,000
I'm the victim.

66
00:03:40,090 --> 00:03:41,320
You are the victim?

67
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,700
Do you think that I don't know that

68
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:45,370
you are swaggering around at school?

69
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:47,050
Tell me,

70
00:03:47,730 --> 00:03:48,940
during your three years
in high school

71
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,579
