72
00:03:51,090 --> 00:03:53,079
Do you want me to

73
00:03:53,170 --> 00:03:54,290
expel you?

74
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:55,870
No.

75
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:59,550
I'm warning you the last time.

76
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,720
If I know

77
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,000
you make trouble at school once again,

78
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,080
I promise that

79
00:04:06,370 --> 00:04:08,480
you'll never have a chance
to get into this school.

80
00:04:08,570 --> 00:04:09,530
Got it?

81
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:11,460
Yes.

82
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:12,430
Say it loudly.

83
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,880
Yes, I got it.

84
00:04:33,370 --> 00:04:35,250
We've been standing here so long.

85
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:38,270
Then,

86
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,070
can I go back to the classroom now?

87
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,120
Come back.

88
00:04:44,450 --> 00:04:46,120
You won't tell me the truth, will you?

89
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:47,950
But,

90
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,210
I've told you everything.

91
00:04:50,490 --> 00:04:52,770
I just bumped into him when I was walking.

92
00:04:52,930 --> 00:04:55,000
It was accidental.

93
00:04:55,090 --> 00:04:56,400
I have apologized to him,

94
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,640
but he just refused to let it go.

95
00:04:57,730 --> 00:04:59,090
What else can I do?

96
00:04:59,590 --> 00:05:01,540
Why did you kick him then?

97
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,240
If what you said is true

98
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:04,480
and you've said sorry to him

99
00:05:04,570 --> 00:05:06,480
why would he go to our classroom
to make trouble?

100
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,610
Do you think it's logical?

101
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,210
I've told you the truth,

102
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,660
but you don't believe me.

103
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,510
So we'll just keep standing here.

104
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,480
Stand here.

105
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,030
Who made the mistake?

106
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,080
You stand.

107
00:05:20,890 --> 00:05:22,520
As a girl,

108
00:05:22,610 --> 00:05:24,880
