109
00:05:24,970 --> 00:05:26,170
Do you think it's right?

110
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:27,460
Mr Wu.

111
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,520
It's me that was bullied.

112
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:33,120
You need to figure out the truth, right?

113
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,790
I can let it go,

114
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,470
but you must promise to me that

115
00:05:40,450 --> 00:05:41,770
you'll focus on your schoolwork.

116
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,100
If he comes and finds
you again, just tell me

117
00:05:43,210 --> 00:05:44,130
and I'll handle it.

118
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:46,360
But you are not allowed to
have conflicts with him again.

119
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,320
Got it?

120
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:48,380
Yes. Thanks, sir.

121
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:49,470
Come back.

122
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,070
By tomorrow afternoon,

123
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,200
write a 300 word self-reflection

124
00:05:53,290 --> 00:05:54,490
and submit it to Ms Yang.

125
00:05:56,010 --> 00:05:56,730
What?

126
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:58,570
You didn't say that.

127
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,560
I'm telling you now.

128
00:06:26,690 --> 00:06:28,240
Just wait and see.

129
00:06:52,050 --> 00:06:53,020
Are you alright?

130
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:53,980
Yeah.

131
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:55,550
Did Mr Wu scold you?

132
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:56,510
No.

133
00:06:57,330 --> 00:06:58,760
How did you get into trouble with him?

134
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,030
Do you two know each other?

135
00:07:00,210 --> 00:07:01,150
No.

136
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,280
It was a misunderstanding.

137
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:03,210
Misunderstanding?

138
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:04,290
Why?

139
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,310
I heard that you just rushed up

140
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,520
and beat him.

141
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,800
Mr Wu had questioned me for 45 minutes.

142
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,910
Are you also questioning me?

143
00:07:12,550 --> 00:07:13,990
-Okay, enough.
-I...

144
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,120
Go back to your seats.

145
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:16,130
Let me talk to her.

146
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:25,450
Don't worry.

147
00:07:25,900 --> 00:07:26,830
As long as I am here,

148
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:29,050
if Chen Jun He dares to find you again,

149
00:07:29,140 --> 00:07:30,020
I'll protect you.

150
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,880
Li Qing Tong.

151
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,409
Everyone can get involved in it

152
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:35,409
except you.

153
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:37,140
Why?

154
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:38,580
You just let it go.

155
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,909
And you are not supposed
to have any contact with him.

156
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,880
This is the rule.

157
00:07:42,210 --> 00:07:43,170
The rule between us.

158
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,159
Do you hear me?

159
00:07:46,530 --> 00:07:47,440
Promise me.

160
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:48,430
Okay?

161
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:52,060
Yeah, okay.

162
00:07:57,850 --> 00:07:58,900
I'll leave you be.

163
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:00,360
Remember.

164
00:08:00,490 --> 00:08:01,900
Don't have any contact with him.

165
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:16,110
Hi, buddy.

166
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,260
We have taken it out for you.

167
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:19,650
Specifically, we have
deflated their bicycle tires.

168
00:08:20,010 --> 00:08:20,890
What?

169
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,250
What have you done?

170
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:24,420
We have deflated their bicycle tires.

171
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:27,340
We don't know which bicycles
belong to Lin Jin Bu and Lin Qing Tong,

172
00:08:27,530 --> 00:08:29,860
so we deflated the tires
of all the bicycles.

173
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,950
This is what they get

174
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:32,809
for making my buddy angry.

175
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:34,159
We are brilliant, right?

176
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,440
What's the matter with you?

177
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,720
Who asked you to do this?

178
00:08:38,309 --> 00:08:39,919
We were letting out your anger.

179
00:08:41,330 --> 00:08:42,880
Don't you feel ashamed to

180
00:08:42,970 --> 00:08:44,240
deflate girls' bicycle tires?

181
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:46,140
Yang Ai Ling is watching me.

182
00:08:46,310 --> 00:08:47,910
Are you asking for me to be expelled?

183
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:48,920
What...

184
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,510
What should we do then?

185
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,840
Go inflate the tires!

186
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:56,690
Chen Jun He.

187
00:09:01,010 --> 00:09:02,720
No matter why Li Jin Bu
got into trouble with you,

188
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:04,110
you just take your anger out

189
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,140
on me.

190
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,490
Don't hurt her.

191
00:09:07,420 --> 00:09:08,520
Hey, buddy.

192
00:09:08,610 --> 00:09:09,600
Are you trying to solve this problem?

193
00:09:09,690 --> 00:09:10,740
No matter what happened,

194
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:12,820
I apologize to you.

195
00:09:15,770 --> 00:09:16,930
It's Li Jin Bu's fault.

196
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,220
Ask her to apologize to me.

197
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:19,530
This is my rule.

198
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,080
Got it?

199
00:09:47,690 --> 00:09:49,090
My bicycle is deflated.

200
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,230
Mine too.

201
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,240
Who did this?

202
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,710
So is mine.

203
00:09:55,820 --> 00:09:57,320
You bicycle is deflated, isn't it?

204
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:00,990
Did you do this?

205
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,540
As if you have caught me.

206
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,450
No one could do this except you.

207
00:10:07,490 --> 00:10:08,560
Yeah, I did.

208
00:10:08,650 --> 00:10:09,530
What can you do?

209
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:13,920
What do you want to do?

210
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,720
You

211
00:10:18,930 --> 00:10:20,680
inflate the tires now

212
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:21,770
and I can let it go.

213
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,230
Who are you?

214
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,700
Why should I do as you told me.

215
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,500
Inflate the tires!

216
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,050
No.

217
00:10:30,250 --> 00:10:31,450
You dare to hit me?

218
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:35,500
Okay. No fighting.

219
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:39,710
Chen Jun He.

220
00:10:40,470 --> 00:10:41,620
We have some conflicts,

221
00:10:42,050 --> 00:10:44,290
so I wouldn't be angry even
if you smashed my bicycle.

222
00:10:44,370 --> 00:10:46,540
But you shouldn't deflate the others.

223
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:49,200
Don't you feel ashamed
to deflate their bikes?

224
00:10:49,290 --> 00:10:50,290
You jerk.

225
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:52,300
You wench.
You dare to call me a jerk?

226
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:54,370
Do you believe I will
pull your hair today?

227
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,400
Chen Jun He is bullying me!

228
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:58,280
Help me!

229
00:10:58,370 --> 00:10:59,480
Help me!

230
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,840
-Help!
-Catch her, quickly!

231
00:11:00,930 --> 00:11:02,040
Chen Jun He is bullying me!

232
00:11:02,130 --> 00:11:03,050
Help!

233
00:11:04,690 --> 00:11:05,600
Stop!

234
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:07,680
Stop.

235
00:11:07,770 --> 00:11:08,650
What are you doing?

236
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:10,220
What are you doing?

237
00:11:10,780 --> 00:11:11,660
Stop there.

238
00:11:12,190 --> 00:11:13,070
What are you doing?

239
00:11:15,530 --> 00:11:16,410
Stop there.

240
00:11:17,690 --> 00:11:18,890
Go home.

241
00:11:19,410 --> 00:11:20,360
What are you doing?

242
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,830
[Learned, Inspired, Educated]

243
00:11:26,190 --> 00:11:27,340
Why are you still here?

244
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,900
Chen Jun He is making trouble again.

245
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,080
What did he do?

246
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,760
Wait for a while.

247
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:36,130
We'll go home after he leaves.

248
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:42,550
You guys, as strong men,

249
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,830
deflated bicycle tires?

250
00:11:45,930 --> 00:11:46,940
Don't you feel ashamed?

251
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,320
This is the last time.

252
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,590
If I see this again,

253
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:51,870
I will punish you severely.

254
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,840
Got it?

255
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:54,520
Yes, Mr Wu.

256
00:11:54,610 --> 00:11:55,750
We will never do it again.

257
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,130
See you, Mr Wu.

258
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:09,410
Buddy.

259
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,320
Humph.

260
00:12:35,850 --> 00:12:37,520
If he didn't inflate the tires for me,

261
00:12:37,620 --> 00:12:39,850
I would beat him unconscious.

262
00:12:40,010 --> 00:12:40,890
Let's go.

263
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:42,920
Listen, I am not afraid of him.

264
00:12:43,010 --> 00:12:45,480
Today, I hit him with my bag.

265
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:48,570
Where is my bag?

266
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,170
Where is my bag?

267
00:12:57,610 --> 00:13:00,600
[Female bath]

268
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:02,690
Where is my uncle?

269
00:13:03,530 --> 00:13:04,410
There.

270
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,650
Cover me.

271
00:13:24,230 --> 00:13:25,400
Stop.

272
00:13:28,610 --> 00:13:29,490
Where are you going?

273
00:13:30,090 --> 00:13:31,040
To scrub the bath.

274
00:13:31,370 --> 00:13:32,570
Not you.

275
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:33,970
Come here.

276
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,840
Uncle.

277
00:13:42,460 --> 00:13:44,220
Why did you come home so late?

278
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:46,780
Today's Niu Xiao Huo's birthday.

279
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,080
I went to his home.

280
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:49,810
Niu Xiao Huo's birthday?

281
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:53,250
Do you think that I don't
know Niu Xiao Huo's birthday?

282
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,840
You changed his birthday?

283
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,650
Uncle, I've got something to do.

284
00:13:57,850 --> 00:13:58,730
Stop.

285
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,390
What's wrong with your bag?

286
00:14:02,490 --> 00:14:03,680
Why do you have a pink bag?

287
00:14:04,650 --> 00:14:05,530
I picked it up.

288
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:08,210
Then give it to your teacher.

289
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:16,500
Stop scrubbing the bath.

290
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,230
Go and do your homework.

291
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,810
Your uncle will scold
you when he's back later.

292
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,310
If I don't do this, he will.

293
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,160
