308
00:15:29,130 --> 00:15:30,010
Don't worry.

309
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,820
I'll take it back for you tomorrow.

310
00:15:32,210 --> 00:15:33,090
No.

311
00:15:33,330 --> 00:15:34,760
You better not clash with him again.

312
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:36,040
