313
00:15:42,170 --> 00:15:42,890
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

314
00:15:42,890 --> 00:15:43,770
Morning, Ms Yang.

315
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:46,600
Morning, Ms Yang.

316
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:49,620
