358
00:18:16,050 --> 00:18:17,280
I'm good at martial arts.

359
00:18:17,410 --> 00:18:18,700
I'm also powerful.

360
00:18:19,020 --> 00:18:20,010
Come on.

361
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:21,800
Just don't respond to him.

362
00:18:22,230 --> 00:18:24,220
