396
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:20,710
No problem.

397
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:22,200
As long as you don't betray me.

398
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,030
Impossible.

399
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:25,640
I'll be the first to say,

400
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:27,000
whoever betrays you,

401
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:28,220
I'll beat him.

402
00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:33,860
I think

403
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,460
