418
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:22,800
Mr Wu,

419
00:21:23,930 --> 00:21:24,810
I didn't

420
00:21:24,940 --> 00:21:25,560
do that.

421
00:21:25,650 --> 00:21:27,000
You didn't do that?

422
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:29,370
