424
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:34,880
Wang Xiao Min, that traitor.

425
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:36,880
I don't want to bother about it anymore.

426
00:21:37,050 --> 00:21:38,850
Ask your aunt to come to school tomorrow.

427
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:39,820
Got it?

428
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:41,660
Ask your aunt to come to school tomorrow.

429
00:21:49,210 --> 00:21:50,610
