439
00:22:15,820 --> 00:22:17,380
Hua, let me explain it to you.

440
00:22:17,730 --> 00:22:18,610
Shameful.

441
00:22:19,520 --> 00:22:20,590
Betrayer.

442
00:22:21,080 --> 00:22:22,370
Traitor!

443
00:22:31,610 --> 00:22:32,620
Mr Wu,

444
00:22:32,970 --> 00:22:34,140
I'm really sorry.

445
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:36,270
We've caused you trouble again.

446
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,010
It's not a big deal.

447
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:39,200
As long as she

448
00:22:39,280 --> 00:22:41,690
