451
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:48,040
I won't apologize.

452
00:22:48,620 --> 00:22:49,500
It's impossible.

453
00:22:50,010 --> 00:22:50,890
Hua.

454
00:22:51,340 --> 00:22:52,660
Don't disrupt

455
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:53,710
