456
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,410
It's fine, Mr Wu.

457
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,000
-I'll go back and reprimand her.
-Alright.

458
00:22:58,090 --> 00:22:59,280
I'll ask her to apologize.

459
00:22:59,370 --> 00:23:00,810
-Good.
-Thanks.

460
00:23:00,910 --> 00:23:02,350
Apologizing is not enough.

461
00:23:03,710 --> 00:23:04,790
Hi, Ms Yang.

462
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:07,870
