478
00:23:45,450 --> 00:23:46,330
Chen Jun He.

479
00:23:46,910 --> 00:23:47,990
What do you want to say?

480
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:50,910
Ms Yang,

481
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:51,970
Mr Wu and auntie,

482
00:23:52,210 --> 00:23:53,310
I think.

483
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:56,840
Li Jin Bu's behaviour is really terrible.

484
00:23:56,940 --> 00:23:58,430
I can look past the trap
she planted

485
00:23:58,530 --> 00:24:00,160
