491
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:11,150
You better stop.

492
00:24:12,010 --> 00:24:12,760
Mr Wu,

493
00:24:12,850 --> 00:24:13,880
I'm the victim.

494
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:15,180
Li Jin Bu has

495
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:17,590
