of more than 5000 words.

505
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:44,630
Reflect on your actions
in Year 3 Class 1.

506
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,110
And apologize to Chen Jun He

507
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,600
in public.

508
00:24:49,990 --> 00:24:51,190
If you can't do these,

509
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:54,120
then you should get out of the school.

510
00:24:54,210 --> 00:24:57,520
This school can't
tolerate students like you.

511
00:25:03,660 --> 00:25:04,920
A little excessive, huh?

512
00:25:05,010 --> 00:25:06,010
Get out.

513
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:11,480
Mr Wu,

514
00:25:11,560 --> 00:25:12,640
I'm really sorry to trouble you.

515
00:25:12,730 --> 00:25:14,370
I'll reprimand her back home.

516
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:15,520
Thanks.

517
00:25:15,760 --> 00:25:16,630
Hua.

518
00:25:16,950 --> 00:25:17,830
Go home.

519
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:20,890
