Come.

524
00:25:43,330 --> 00:25:44,700
I want to have a talk with you.

525
00:25:54,310 --> 00:25:55,190
Hua.

526
00:25:55,930 --> 00:25:56,650
You

527
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:58,700
