555
00:26:49,370 --> 00:26:50,930
Come on.

556
00:26:51,010 --> 00:26:52,940
Don't gossip in front of kids.

557
00:26:53,140 --> 00:26:54,750
It's not gossip. It's true.

558
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:55,480
I...

559
00:26:55,570 --> 00:26:58,330
I'm telling them that
the problem is serious.

560
00:26:58,500 --> 00:27:00,070
Come on. We know.

561
00:27:00,150 --> 00:27:01,100
Let's have dinner.

562
00:27:01,230 --> 00:27:02,470
-Have dinner.
-Stand up.

563
00:27:03,410 --> 00:27:04,410
