and do your homework.

584
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:47,630
Li Qing Tong,

585
00:27:47,730 --> 00:27:49,660
you won't be eating dinner tonight.

586
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:50,810
You are terribly spoilt.

587
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:51,840
You...

588
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,890
You should let her have dinner.

589
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,680
I'm sorry, auntie.

590
00:27:57,890 --> 00:27:58,760
I'm really sorry.

591
00:27:58,850 --> 00:28:01,090
I assure you that I won't do it again.

592
00:28:05,690 --> 00:28:07,360
You should

593
00:28:07,450 --> 00:28:08,510
let them have dinner.

594
00:28:08,610 --> 00:28:10,240
Don't be so angry.

595
00:28:10,330 --> 00:28:11,700
I'm going to scold you too.

596
00:28:12,950 --> 00:28:13,940
What's wrong with me?

597
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:15,270
You know what you have done.

598
00:28:15,690 --> 00:28:16,770
Our daughter

599
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:18,260
is terribly spoilt by you.

600
00:28:18,410 --> 00:28:19,040
That brat.

601
00:28:19,130 --> 00:28:20,750
I barely said anything to her

602
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,070
and look how she reacted?

603
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,090
This is bad.

604
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:27,610
Once she starts,

605
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:29,420
she won't stop any time soon.

606
00:28:29,510 --> 00:28:31,690
How long does such situation last?

607
00:28:31,780 --> 00:28:32,850
One or two days to

608
00:28:32,940 --> 00:28:34,140
one or two weeks.

609
00:28:34,770 --> 00:28:37,170
It mainly depends on
how my father pacifies her.

610
00:28:37,430 --> 00:28:38,660
Fortunately, you're not like that.

611
00:28:39,190 --> 00:28:40,140
Me?

612
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:43,590
I have no right to lose
my temper at my home.

613
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:45,500
Only my mum has the right.

614
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:48,000
My family is better.

615
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:50,050
At least I have the
right to lose my temper.

616
00:28:50,150 --> 00:28:51,430
Does your mother scold you?

617
00:28:52,580 --> 00:28:53,460
Of course.

618
00:28:53,870 --> 00:28:55,340
But only for a short while.

619
00:28:55,600 --> 00:28:57,150
And she has a virtue where

620
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:58,570
she'd forget everything

621
00:28:58,670 --> 00:28:59,770
after a night of sleep.

622
00:29:00,930 --> 00:29:02,130
That's like me.

623
00:29:02,970 --> 00:29:03,880
Never hold grudges,

624
00:29:03,990 --> 00:29:04,870
easy to coax.

625
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,360
What a coincidence.

626
00:29:09,230 --> 00:29:12,320
But not everything
you said is true, isn't it?

627
00:29:12,770 --> 00:29:13,650
What do you mean?

628
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:14,800
What do you mean?

629
00:29:16,330 --> 00:29:18,200
You mean that I have no
right to criticize your daughter?

630
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:19,640
Even a word is not allowed?

631
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:23,400
Of course you have the right.

632
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:24,200
You are the boss.

633
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:25,530
You are always right.

634
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,780
Li Wu Si,

635
00:29:29,070 --> 00:29:31,260
Li Qing Tong is the way she is
because of you.

636
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:34,350
Go on and spoil her more.

637
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:35,550
You continue.

638
00:29:35,770 --> 00:29:36,480
I'll see

639
00:29:36,570 --> 00:29:38,450
how much worse she'd become.

640
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:43,310
What...

641
00:29:43,570 --> 00:29:44,710
What does it have to do with me?

642
00:29:45,280 --> 00:29:46,840
Aren't you eating dinner?

643
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,480
What should we do.

644
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:02,670
It's a mess in school.

645
00:30:02,970 --> 00:30:04,170
It's a mess at home.

646
00:30:05,580 --> 00:30:07,610
Don't think so much.

647
00:30:07,700 --> 00:30:08,930
Do your homework.

648
00:30:09,710 --> 00:30:11,430
I don't have the

649
00:30:11,620 --> 00:30:12,850
mood to study.

650
00:30:12,940 --> 00:30:14,410
I can't study now.

651
00:30:15,990 --> 00:30:16,870
Study.

652
00:30:18,700 --> 00:30:19,450
If you don't study,

653
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:20,650
I'll tell your mum.

654
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:22,520
Aun...

655
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,370
Give it to me.

656
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,580
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

657
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,390
Can I talk to you?

658
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,120
No.

659
00:30:48,270 --> 00:30:50,380
Could you ask Yang Ai Ling

660
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:52,950
to stop getting involved with the
conflict between you and Li Jin Bu.

661
00:30:53,040 --> 00:30:54,080
I tell Yang Ai Ling?

662
00:30:54,210 --> 00:30:55,290
Why she would agree?

663
00:30:55,970 --> 00:30:58,050
She is asking Lin Jin Bu
to say sorry to you.

664
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:00,070
If you tell her that you
have forgiven Li Jin Bu,

665
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,430
she would probably let it go.

666
00:31:02,050 --> 00:31:02,930
Firstly.

667
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:05,600
Yang Ai Ling is angry because Li
Jin Bu drew an ugly picture of her.

668
00:31:05,690 --> 00:31:06,320
Secondly,

669
00:31:06,410 --> 00:31:07,640
why should I forgive
her without her apology?

670
00:31:07,730 --> 00:31:09,200
She is supposed to say sorry to me.

671
00:31:09,290 --> 00:31:11,050
Don't forget that she hit me on my face.

672
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:13,850
She should apologize to
me for what she has done.

673
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,320
What if I apologize to you for her?

674
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,320
No.

675
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:35,450
Read it in your class

676
00:31:35,530 --> 00:31:37,540
and also in Year 3 Class 1.

677
00:31:37,830 --> 00:31:38,570
Why?

678
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,540
Why?

679
00:31:42,210 --> 00:31:43,520
Is this the way

680
00:31:43,630 --> 00:31:45,830
you should speak to a teacher?

681
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:48,890
I'm sorry.

682
00:31:50,090 --> 00:31:50,970
Lin Jin Bu.

683
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:54,080
You only have one day.

684
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:56,270
If you don't read it today,

685
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:58,180
don't bother coming to school tomorrow.

686
00:31:58,630 --> 00:31:59,510
Got it.

687
00:32:07,660 --> 00:32:08,480
Hua.

688
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:11,530
I think you'd better
apologize to Chen Jun He.

689
00:32:11,970 --> 00:32:13,160
It's not a big deal.

690
00:32:13,290 --> 00:32:14,170
No.

691
00:32:15,190 --> 00:32:17,550
You should be sensible.

692
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:20,920
You hit him on his face, didn't you?

693
00:32:21,290 --> 00:32:22,410
It's your fault.

694
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:25,080
Who are you helping?

695
00:32:26,700 --> 00:32:28,770
I'm trying to find a way
to solve this problem.

696
00:32:29,380 --> 00:32:31,070
Now, at school,

697
00:32:31,170 --> 00:32:32,350
you've offended Chen Jun He

698
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,710
as well as Yang Ai Ling.

699
00:32:34,090 --> 00:32:36,330
What if they continue to make trouble
for you?

700
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,570
Then I'll drop out of school.

701
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:38,540
It doesn't matter.

702
00:32:38,670 --> 00:32:39,980
You are not reasonable.

703
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:41,180
I'm reasonable.

704
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,590
No, you are not.

705
00:32:45,770 --> 00:32:47,010
I think

706
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:48,970
you should be reasonable.

707
00:32:49,650 --> 00:32:51,160
And you always refuse to

708
00:32:51,250 --> 00:32:53,840
tell me the reason for the conflict
between you and Chen Jun He.

709
00:32:53,930 --> 00:32:55,470
Do you take me as your best friend?

710
00:32:56,760 --> 00:32:57,640
Fine.

711
00:32:57,890 --> 00:32:58,850
You go and find him.

712
00:32:59,210 --> 00:33:00,090
You are so silly

713
00:33:00,250 --> 00:33:01,500
that you are cheated by him.

714
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:03,610
I'm silly?

715
00:33:03,700 --> 00:33:04,580
I'm silly?

716
00:33:04,670 --> 00:33:05,660
And you're smart?

717
00:33:05,810 --> 00:33:06,800
Your trick

718
00:33:06,890 --> 00:33:08,690
got yourself in trouble.

719
00:33:12,020 --> 00:33:12,790
Mum!

720
00:33:12,890 --> 00:33:13,680
I'm not your mum.

721
00:33:13,770 --> 00:33:14,650
Your mum is dead.

722
00:33:15,930 --> 00:33:17,240
Why do you say that?

723
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:19,230
It's not auspicious. Mum!

724
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:25,780
Honey.

725
00:33:25,870 --> 00:33:26,460
We're hungry.

726
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:27,420
Stay hungry.

727
00:33:28,530 --> 00:33:29,730
There's no dinner tonight.

728
00:33:32,080 --> 00:33:33,180
Mum!

729
00:33:38,610 --> 00:33:41,210
Dad, I'm hungry.

730
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:05,600
Let's go.

731
00:34:05,850 --> 00:34:07,210
We're going to eat out.

732
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:08,880
Go.

733
00:34:14,560 --> 00:34:16,870
[Daily Neccessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

734
00:34:16,870 --> 00:34:19,429
[Today: Chicken feet special,
buy one free one]

735
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:34,080
I think that they are
reluctant to talk to me recently.

736
00:34:34,170 --> 00:34:35,710
I don't want to talk to you either.

737
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:38,260
But, Xiao,

738
00:34:38,969 --> 00:34:40,480
it' not all my fault.

739
00:34:41,090 --> 00:34:42,159
I

740
00:34:42,260 --> 00:34:44,179
was threatened by Chen Jun He.

741
00:34:44,690 --> 00:34:46,080
I had no choice
but to disclose the secret.

742
00:34:46,170 --> 00:34:47,130
Come on.

743
00:34:47,250 --> 00:34:48,370
Stop talking about it.

744
00:34:49,080 --> 00:34:49,960
Do you

745
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,989
know why Lin Jin Bu

746
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,560
hit Chen Jun He on his face?

747
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:56,150
Even Li Qing Tong doesn't know.

748
00:34:56,250 --> 00:34:57,730
How can I know?

749
00:34:59,340 --> 00:35:00,660
I just think it's a bit weird.

750
00:35:01,390 --> 00:35:03,400
She just came back recently

751
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,750
and we're not in the same year
as Chen Jun He.

752
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:07,100
Thus

753
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:08,510
they shouldn't have conflicts.

754
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:09,480
Right?

755
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:11,570
But why are they so against each other?

756
00:35:12,680 --> 00:35:13,560
Maybe...

757
00:35:14,370 --> 00:35:16,090
Maybe something happened previously.

758
00:35:16,180 --> 00:35:17,740
It's obvious that she is seeking revenge.

759
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:20,380
What conflicts could they have?

760
00:35:21,730 --> 00:35:23,770
Don't bother trying to figure
things out related to women.

761
00:35:23,910 --> 00:35:25,320
Those things are so complicated.

762
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:28,760
It seems that you know a lot.

763
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:31,720
I know much more than you.

764
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:34,890
I've found out the basic
rules from my mum.

765
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:36,840
If

766
00:35:37,970 --> 00:35:38,850
she says that

767
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:40,140
she isn't angry,

768
00:35:40,490 --> 00:35:41,510
then she must be angry.

769
00:35:42,090 --> 00:35:43,940
If she says
she doesn't want to eat it,

770
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,490
then you shouldn't eat it either.

771
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,320
If she says that it doesn't matter,

772
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:49,060
then she must be furious.

773
00:35:50,120 --> 00:35:51,640
If she says that she's
put on weight recently,

774
00:35:51,730 --> 00:35:53,920
you must say that she is slim.

775
00:35:54,010 --> 00:35:56,600
If she complains to you about someone,

776
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:59,620
don't ask who it is.

777
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:01,160
Just complain along with her.

778
00:36:02,990 --> 00:36:05,310
My dad and I survive this way.

779
00:36:06,290 --> 00:36:07,210
So,

780
00:36:07,290 --> 00:36:09,010
you should know how they think.

781
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:10,840
Don't say anything that you shouldn't say.

782
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,430
Don't ask about anything
that you shouldn't know.

783
00:36:12,530 --> 00:36:13,690
I don't agree with you.

784
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:15,590
My mum is different.

785
00:36:15,690 --> 00:36:16,960
My mum tells us what
she's thinking directly.

786
00:36:17,050 --> 00:36:17,960
That's why.

787
00:36:18,210 --> 00:36:20,730
Your mum and mine are different species.

788
00:36:21,370 --> 00:36:23,060
Together with those girls,

789
00:36:24,090 --> 00:36:26,080
it would take us a long
time to figure them out.

790
00:36:37,130 --> 00:36:38,010
Li Jin Bu.

791
00:37:20,410 --> 00:37:21,550
Dear teachers

792
00:37:21,640 --> 00:37:22,610
and schoolmates.

793
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:26,370
I wrote this self-reflection today

794
00:37:26,640 --> 00:37:29,200
to reflect upon my mistakes.

795
00:37:29,650 --> 00:37:32,050
I've thought a lot

796
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,690
about what I've done.

797
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:34,930
I feel regretful

798
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:36,510
for breaking the rules.

799
00:37:36,930 --> 00:37:39,850
I know that I've
made a serious mistake

800
00:37:40,120 --> 00:37:42,560
and I'm ashamed of my mistake.

801
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:48,150
Finally,

802
00:37:48,330 --> 00:37:51,040
I want to express my
sincerest apology to Ms Yang.

803
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:54,600
I'm sorry to have let you down.

804
00:37:58,160 --> 00:37:59,360
Chen Jun He,

805
00:37:59,610 --> 00:38:00,890
I have something to tell you.

806
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:03,940
I blew it this time,

807
00:38:04,190 --> 00:38:05,720
but I'd never say sorry to you.

808
00:38:06,390 --> 00:38:07,620
I just want to say that

809
00:38:08,350 --> 00:38:09,270
you deserve it.

810
00:38:20,050 --> 00:38:21,250
Interesting.

811
00:38:51,090 --> 00:38:51,970
Hua.

812
00:38:52,420 --> 00:38:54,170
You shouldn't be too
stubborn under such situation.

813
00:38:54,290 --> 00:38:56,050
We should know how to minimize the loss.

814
00:38:57,250 --> 00:38:58,920
I don't know how to explain it to you.

815
00:38:59,690 --> 00:39:01,060
But I really dislike him.

816
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,960
Well, well, well.

817
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:07,450
What are you doing?

818
00:39:08,950 --> 00:39:10,750
I don't know why you hit me on my face,

819
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,160
but it doesn't matter.

820
00:39:12,290 --> 00:39:13,880
Since you dislike me,

821
00:39:13,970 --> 00:39:15,250
I won't hold back either.

822
00:39:15,670 --> 00:39:17,600
Now, I will let the whole school know

823
00:39:17,690 --> 00:39:20,130
that you're as terrible as me.

824
00:39:20,410 --> 00:39:23,370
We would often have conflicts.

825
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:25,220
We are both bad students.

826
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:27,950
The worst outcome is
that we're both expelled.

827
00:39:28,720 --> 00:39:30,530
I don't care about it.

828
00:39:32,450 --> 00:39:33,530
Me either.

829
00:39:38,730 --> 00:39:39,610
Chen Jun He,

830
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,160
you are too much.

831
00:39:42,290 --> 00:39:44,170
She said that I deserved it.

832
00:39:44,490 --> 00:39:46,920
Then I'll show you how I deserve it.

833
00:39:49,860 --> 00:39:50,740
Everyone,

834
00:39:51,070 --> 00:39:52,110
don't leave after school.

835
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:53,270
Let's go home together.

836
00:39:58,000 --> 00:39:59,320
Humph.

837
00:39:59,670 --> 00:40:00,940
Look at the way he swaggers.

838
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,360
Oh my God.

839
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:05,040
This time we really pissed him off.

840
00:40:05,130 --> 00:40:07,050
Things will be tough from here on out.

841
00:40:07,130 --> 00:40:08,150
Don't be afraid of him.

842
00:40:08,390 --> 00:40:09,750
He can't do nothing to us.

843
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,480
What's up?

844
00:40:29,500 --> 00:40:31,170
I want to solve this problem with you.

845
00:40:32,080 --> 00:40:32,960
Solve this problem?

846
00:40:33,560 --> 00:40:34,520
How?

847
00:40:35,790 --> 00:40:37,930
Lin Jin Bu is studying here because of me.

848
00:40:38,020 --> 00:40:39,420
I have to be responsible for her.

849
00:40:39,510 --> 00:40:40,570
The conflicts between you and Li Jin Bu

850
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,780
should be solved now.

851
00:40:43,180 --> 00:40:44,060
I can't do much.

852
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:46,180
But I can apologize on her behalf.

853
00:40:46,910 --> 00:40:47,790
With this,

854
00:40:48,110 --> 00:40:50,040
the grudge between you two
is cleared.

855
00:40:50,140 --> 00:40:51,020
Okay?

856
00:40:53,300 --> 00:40:54,250
I told you.

857
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:56,610
Whoever did it should bear
the responsibility.

858
00:40:56,700 --> 00:40:58,050
Ask her

859
00:40:58,220 --> 00:40:59,240
to say sorry to me.

860
00:40:59,540 --> 00:41:01,420
You have your rules and I have my rules.

861
00:41:03,630 --> 00:41:04,550
Give me your shoe.

862
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:08,920
What are you afraid of?

863
00:41:09,010 --> 00:41:10,240
So many people are watching.

864
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,800
Take off your shoe.

865
00:41:13,210 --> 00:41:14,090
Okay.

866
00:41:17,880 --> 00:41:18,760
Here you go.
